      "text": "Putt & Putter is a miniature golf video game released for the Master System in June 1992 and Game Gear in December 1991.  It was developed by SIMS Co, and published by Sega. In Brazil the game was called Mini-Golf. The back of the box describes it as a cross between mini-golf and pinball.",
